verbose_text: However, the cellular cholesterol efflux in the peritoneal macrophages and hepatocytes, as induced by HDL, correlated with the protein expression level of ABCA1 and SR-B1 (data not shown) (in peritoneal macrophages, r = 0.701, P = 0.001; r = 0.786, P < 0.001, respectively; and in hepatocytes, r = 0.763, P < 0.001; r = 0.813, P < 0.001; respectively).
